ialog", "role": "米莎", "content": "即使只有一步，我也要......踏出这一步。"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "米莎", "content": "对不起，阿米娅，对不起......"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "米莎", "content": "整合运动是感染者......"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "米莎", "content": "他们，也是感染者啊......"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "米莎", "content": "再见了......"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "阿米娅", "content": "米莎？米莎？！米莎！！"}, {"id": 0, "type": "dialog", "role": "阿米娅", "content": "......"}]